model.name: Scarf Print Asymmetrical Midi Skirt
model.disambiguatingDescription: A chic Louis Vuitton silhouette returns in this season’s striking scarf print of archival bag details. Crafted from airy silk twill, this midi skirt is cut with asymmetrical pleats that underscore the fluidity of the fabric. The exposed two-way side zipper can be styled open for a sensual look, while an ornate button adds an essential seasonal detail.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• Length : 76,4 cm / 30,1 inches
  • Main Material : 100% Silk
  • Lining : 100% Silk
  • Grey
  • Regular fit
  • Made in France
  • Do not wash
  • Do not bleach
  • Do not tumble dry
  • Iron at a maximum sole-plate temperature of 110°C
  • Mild professionnal dry cleaning in hydrocarbons
